-- JOBS_SEQEUENCENUMBERS < 10000 free for rebuilding the sequence,
-- which will be made in the second step.
-- ATTENTION:
The first row in table JOBS get the number 10001, the second 10002 and
so on. After all rows < 10000 will be executed the first number
> 10000 will be executed, if 'normal' is selected in the
DB_TABLES, column OPEN, but this row was already updated.
So the task will be closed if all rows < 10000 will be executed, see EndTask-Cnd
